  "description": "n8n governance dashboard. Surfaces three customer-impact patterns the platform-team failed to catch in the past: quota overrun, high-failure-rate workflows, and unattended (\"zombie\") workflows still running months after deployment. Drill into a single workflow or project with the $workflow and $project variables. $quota is an editable numeric textbox that colors the Quota Consumed gauge.",
