      "description": "Workflows that have been active and running for more than 30 days, AND have NOT been edited in the last 30 days. These are 'zombies' \u2014 running unattended, no one is reviewing them. Matches the demo-workflow-ran-4-months pattern. The days_since_edit column is colored red when high.",
